query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('aspnetboilerplate',
'crashlytics',
'forms-authentication',
'hdf5',
'imap',
'kendo-asp.net-mvc',
'odoo-10',
'opera',
'postback',
'shared-memory',
'tridion');
